data.description:
Welcome to your dream home at Sims Landing! This immaculate FIVE BEDROOM, 4 FULL BATHROOM residence is the epitome of move-in ready, sparing you the wait of construction delays! Boasting a spacious 3025 square feet, this home has been meticulously maintained, and it shows. 
The heart of the home is the generously sized living room, featuring a cozy FIREPLACE - the perfect spot to unwind on chilly evenings. In addition to the main living areas, relish the luxury of an EXTRA SPACIOUS FAMILY ROOM UPSTAIRS, providing ample space for various activities.
Rest easy knowing that the recently installed roof provides an additional level of assurance, safeguarding your investment for the long term. Also enjoy the added convenience of an electric car charging port in the garage! 
With proximity to FORT GORDON, GROVETOWN, and DOWNTOWN AUGUSTA, convenience is at your doorstep. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this BEAUTIFUL, well-kept home yours. Schedule your viewing today! Seller is offering $5000 towards a rate buy down or closing cost, or ask us about the assumable VA loan sitting under 3%!
